.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/gpu-%EC%84%9C%EB%B2%84-%EA%B8%B0%EC%B4%88-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/22/gpu-서버-기초-정리.png" type="image/png" length="14276" /> </item> <item> <title>NVLink와 노드 안 GPU 연결 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>노드 안 GPU를 잇는 NVLink 세대별 대역폭과 NVSwitch·GPUDirect P2P·Fabric Manager 역할, PCIe와의 차이를 표로 비교 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/nvlink%EC%99%80-%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C-%EC%95%88-gpu-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 21:02:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/nvlink%EC%99%80-%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C-%EC%95%88-gpu-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/22/nvlink와-노드-안-gpu-연결-정리.png" type="image/png" length="16762" /> </item> <item> <title>분산 학습 병렬화와 집합 통신 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>집합 통신 연산과 Data·Tensor·Pipeline·Expert 병렬화, ZeRO·FSDP 샤딩, 병렬화별 NVLink·InfiniBand 링크 매핑을 표로 비교</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B3%91%EB%A0%AC%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 21:02:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B3%91%EB%A0%AC%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blo