ub.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/nic-%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%BB%A4%EB%84%90-%EB%B0%94%EC%9D%B4%ED%8C%A8%EC%8A%A4-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 21:02:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/nic-%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%BB%A4%EB%84%90-%EB%B0%94%EC%9D%B4%ED%8C%A8%EC%8A%A4-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/22/nic-가상화와-커널-바이패스-정리.png" type="image/png" length="13507" /> </item> <item> <title>OpenTelemetry 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>SRE</category> <description>OpenTelemetry의 신호 3종, API·SDK·Collector·OTLP 구성, 수동·자동 계측과 head·tail 샘플링, Collector 배포 패턴까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 21:02:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-정리.png" type="image/png" length="17237" /> </item> <item> <title>OpenTelemetry Collector로 분산 트레이싱 실습</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>SRE</category> <description>OpenTelemetry Collector와 Jaeger를 docker compose로 세워 Flask 두 서비스의 요청이 traceparent로 한 trace에 묶이는지 zero-code 계측으로 실측한 기록</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/20/opentelemetry-collector%EB%A1%9C-%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0-%ED%8A%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%8B%B1-%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 21:02:21 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_updated.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/